description: There are a couple of things you do not do in life. You don't try to drive your car blindfolded. You don't try a free fall from 15000ft. with your new homemade flying suit. And you certainly do not want to call The Ninja "A prissy little bitch" then go on to say you going to kick her ass. Attend.
title: The Ninja (3-0) vs. The Vixen (0-1)
